1265
02:13:58,400 --> 02:13:59,905
Možda bi hteo da uzmes ovo...

1266
02:14:08,700 --> 02:14:11,249
Hvala vam puno za ovo, gospodine...

1267
02:14:15,000 --> 02:14:16,213
I ovo.

1268
02:14:25,800 --> 02:14:28,267
Ne, ne, ne treba.

1269
02:14:28,500 --> 02:14:29,893
On tebi pripada.

1270
02:14:31,300 --> 02:14:33,814
